Class NodeMap

java.lang.Object
  resources.RootClass
      metabase.NodeMap

 class NodeMap
extends RootClass

This class wraps a LinkedHashMap of TAP nodes. Each node is referenced by a key (a String) either computed by @see computeKey or given by the caller.
